&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a leader who can combine operational excellence with vision, influence and transformational thinking. Someone who can shape the future of the studio by building smart systems, scalable workflows, effective resource models and a high-performing culture that enables creative teams to use their strengths.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role goes beyond optimisation. We are not looking for someone to simply maintain existing ways of working. We are looking for someone who can challenge the status quo, bring fresh thinking and lead meaningful change.&lt;/p&gt;
