&lt;p&gt;Success in this role will require strong leadership presence, sound judgement and the ability to influence and align stakeholders with differing priorities. You will be comfortable making difficult decisions, driving momentum and leading teams through periods of change, while bringing people with you on the journey.&lt;/p&gt;
