&lt;li&gt;Create clarity and visibility across how work flows from early concept through to delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement new workflows and operating models that allow seamless collaboration across studio, client engagement, production and delivery teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promote a proactive, data-informed approach to resourcing, forecasting and utilisation&lt;/li&gt;
